participant_id.Description: Unique BIDS identifier for the participant in this study.

YSR_01.LongName: I act too young for my age

YSR_02a.LongName: I drink alcohol without my parents' approval

YSR_04.LongName: I fail to finish things that I start

YSR_05.LongName: There is very little that I enjoy

YSR_08.LongName: I have trouble concentrating or paying attention

YSR_9a.LongName: I can't get my mind off certain thoughts

YSR_13.LongName: I feel confused or in a fog

YSR_18.LongName: I deliberately try to hurt or kill myself

YSR_19.LongName: I try to get a lot of attention

YSR_21.LongName: I destroy things belonging to others

YSR_24.LongName: I don't eat as well as I should

YSR_25.LongName: I don't get along with other kids

YSR_26.LongName: I don't feel guilty after doing something I shouldn't

YSR_28.LongName: I break rules at home, school, or elsewhere

YSR_29a.LongName: I am afraid of certain animals, situations, or places, other than school

YSR_30.LongName: I am afraid of going to school

YSR_31.LongName: I am afraid I might think or do something bad

YSR_32.LongName: I feel that I have to be perfect

YSR_33.LongName: I feel that no one loves me

YSR_34.LongName: I feel that others are out to get me

YSR_36.LongName: I accidentally get hurt a lot

YSR_39.LongName: I hang around with kids who get in trouble

YSR_40a.LongName: I hear sounds or voices that other people think aren't there

YSR_41.LongName: I act without stopping to think

YSR_42.LongName: I would rather be alone than with others

YSR_46a.LongName: Parts of my body twitch or make nervous movements

YSR_48.LongName: I am not liked by other kids

YSR_49.LongName: I can do certain things better than most kids

YSR_50.LongName: I am too fearful or anxious

YSR_54.LongName: I feel overtired without good reason

YSR_56a.LongName: Aches or pains (not stomach or headaches)

YSR_56d1.LongName: Problems with eyes (not if corrected by glasses)

YSR_58a.LongName: I pick my skin or other parts of my body

YSR_60.LongName: I like to try new things

YSR_62.LongName: I am poorly coordinated or clumsy

YSR_63.LongName: I would rather be with older kids than kids my own age

YSR_64.LongName: I would rather be with younger kids than kids my own age

YSR_66a.LongName: I repeat certain acts over and over

YSR_69.LongName: I am secretive or keep things to myself

YSR_70a.LongName: I see things that other people think aren't there

YSR_71.LongName: I am self-conscious or easily embarrassed

YSR_73.LongName: I can work well with my hands

YSR_75.LongName: I am too shy or timid

YSR_76.LongName: I sleep less than most kids

YSR_77a.LongName: I sleep more than most kids during day and/or night

YSR_78.LongName: I am inattentive or easily distracted

YSR_80.LongName: I stand up for my rights

YSR_82.LongName: I steal from places other than home

YSR_83a.LongName: I store up too  many things I don't need

YSR_84a.LongName: I do things other people think are strange

YSR_85a.LongName: I have thoughts that other people would think are strange

YSR_87.LongName: My moods or feelings change suddenly

YSR_90.LongName: I swear or use dirty language

YSR_92.LongName: I like to make others laugh

YSR_96.LongName: I think about sex too much

YSR_99.LongName: I smoke, chew, or sniff tobacco

YSR_101.LongName: I cut classes or skip school

YSR_103.LongName: I am unhappy, sad, or depressed

YSR_104.LongName: I am louder than other kids

YSR_105a.LongName: I use drugs for nonmedical purposes (don't include alcohol or tobacco)

YSR_106.LongName: I like to be fair to others

YSR_108.LongName: I like to take life easy

YSR_109.LongName: I try to help other people when I can

YSR_110.LongName: I wish I were of the opposite sex

YSR_111.LongName: I keep from getting involved with others

YSR_113.Description: Sum of scores of items 14-Cries a lot, 29-Fears, 30-Fears school, 31-Fears doing bad, 32-Must be perfect, 33-Feels unloved, 35-Feels worthless, 45-Nervous, tense, 50-Fearful, anxious, 52-Feels too guilty, 71-Self-conscious, 91-Talks or thinks of suicide, 112-Worries. | Calculation = [YSR_14] + [YSR_29a] + [YSR_30] + [YSR_31] + [YSR_32] + [YSR_33] + [YSR_35] + [YSR_45] + [YSR_50] + [YSR_52] + [YSR_71] + [YSR_91] + [YSR_112]

YSR_114.Description: Sum of scores of items 5-Enjoys little, 42-Rather be alone, 65-Won’t talk, 69-Secretive, 75-Shy, timid, 102-Lacks energy, 103-Sad, 111-Withdrawn. | Calculation = [YSR_05] + [YSR_42] + [YSR_65] + [YSR_69] + [YSR_75] + [YSR_102] + [YSR_103] + [YSR_111]

YSR_115.Description: Sum of scores of items 47-Nightmares, 51-Feels dizzy, 54-Overtired, 56a-Aches, pains, 56b-Headaches, 56c-Nausea, 56d-Eye Problems, 56e-Skin Problems, 56f-Stomachaches, 56g-Vomiting. | Calculation = [YSR_47] + [YSR_51] + [YSR_54] + [YSR_56a] + [YSR_56b] + [YSR_56c] + [YSR_56d1] + [YSR_56e] + [YSR_56f] + [YSR_56g]

YSR_116.Description: Sum of scores of items 11-Too dependent, 12-Lonely, 25-Doesn’t get along, 27-Jealous, 34-Others out to get him/her, 36-Accident-prone, 38-Gets teased, 48-Not liked, 62-Clumsy, 64-Prefers younger kids, 79-Speech problems. | Calculation = [YSR_11] + [YSR_12] + [YSR_25] + [YSR_27] + [YSR_34] + [YSR_36] + [YSR_38] + [YSR_48] + [YSR_62] + [YSR_64] + [YSR_79a]

YSR_117.Description: Sum of scores of items 9-Can’t get mind off thoughts, 18-Harms self, 40-Hears things, 46-Twitching, 58-Picks skin, 66-Repeats acts, 70-Sees things, 76-Sleeps less, 83-Stores things, 84-Strange behavior, 85-Strange ideas, 100-Trouble sleeping. | Calculation = [YSR_9a] + [YSR_18] + [YSR_40a] + [YSR_46a] + [YSR_58a] + [YSR_66a] + [YSR_70a] + [YSR_76] + [YSR_83a] + [YSR_84a] + [YSR_85a] + [YSR_100a]

YSR_118.Description: Sum of scores of items 1-Acts young, 4-Fails to finish, 8-Can’t concentrate, 10-Can’t sit still, 13-Confused, 17-Daydreams, 41-Impulsive, 61-Poor schoolwork, 78-Inattentive. | Calculation = [YSR_01] + [YSR_04] + [YSR_08] + [YSR_10] + [YSR_13] + [YSR_17] + [YSR_41] + [YSR_61] + [YSR_78]

YSR_119.Description: Sum of scores of items 2-Drinks alcohol, 26-Lacks guilt, 28-Breaks rules, 39-Bad friends, 43-Lies, cheats, 63-Prefers older kids, 67-Runs away, 72-Sets fires, 81-Steals at home, 82-Steals outside home, 90-Swearing, 96-Thinks of sex too much, 99-Uses tobacco, 101-Truant, 105-Uses drugs. | Calculation = [YSR_02a] + [YSR_26] + [YSR_28] + [YSR_39] + [YSR_43] + [YSR_63] + [YSR_67] + [YSR_72] + [YSR_81] + [YSR_82] + [YSR_90] + [YSR_96] + [YSR_99] + [YSR_101] + [YSR_105a]

YSR_120.Description: Sum of scores of items 3-Argues a lot, 16-Mean to others, 19-Demands attention, 20-Destroys own things, 21-Destroys others’ things, 22-Disobedient at home, 23-Disobedient at school, 37-Gets in fights, 57-Attacks people, 68-Screams a lot, 86-Stubborn, sullen, 87-Mood changes, 89-Suspicious, 94-Teases a lot, 95-Temper, 97-Threatens others, 104-Loud. | Calculation = [YSR_03] + [YSR_16] + [YSR_19] + [YSR_20] + [YSR_21] + [YSR_22] + [YSR_23] + [YSR_37] + [YSR_57] + [YSR_68] + [YSR_86] + [YSR_87] + [YSR_89] + [YSR_94] + [YSR_95] + [YSR_97] + [YSR_104]

YSR_121.Description: Sum of scores of items 7-Bragging, boasting, 24-Doesn’t eat well, 44-Bites finger nails, 53-Overeating, 55-Overweight, 56h-Other physical, 74-Showing off, clowning, 77-Sleeps more, 93-Talks too much, 110-Wishes to be opposite sex. | Calculation = [YSR_07] + [YSR_24] + [YSR_44] + [YSR_53] + [YSR_55] + [YSR_56h1] + [YSR_74] + [YSR_77a] + [YSR_93] + [YSR_110]

YSR_122.Description: Sum of Anxious/Depressed, Withdrawn/Depressed, and Somatic Complaints Subscores. This grouping is called “Internalizing,” because it comprises problems that are mainly within the self. | Calculation = [YSR_113] + [YSR_114] + [YSR_115]

YSR_123.Description: Sum of Rule-Breaking Behavior and Aggressive Behavior Subscores. This grouping is called “Externalizing,” because it comprises problems that mainly involve conflicts with other people and with their expectations for the child. | Calculation = [YSR_119] + [YSR_120]

YSR_124.Description: Sum of Social Problems, Thought Problems, Attention Problems, and Other Problems subscores. | Calculation = [YSR_116] + [YSR_117] + [YSR_118] + [YSR_121]

YSR_125.Description: Sum of Social Problems, Thought Problems, Attention Problems, Other Problems, Internalizing Behaviors and Externalizing Behaviors. A child’s Total Problems score can range from 0 (if the respondent scored every problem 0) to 224 (if the respondent scored every problem 2). | Calculation = [YSR_122] + [YSR_123] + [YSR_124]
